Description: Naruto, ninja in training, learns more about his destiny and the fate of his universe.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 50
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: The next generation of Yu-Gi-Oh battle it out at the Duel Academy. But what evil plans are afoot?
Title: YU-GI-OH! GX, VOL. 6
Author: Naoyuki Kageyama

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, danger lurks nearby for Ichigo and his friends.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 34
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human? In this volume: butler vs. butler!
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 4
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 5
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Misao Harada can see the magic hidden in the world, but it turns out to be a a power that demons wants to exploit. Will her childhood friend, Kyo, who is the head of a demon clan, help or hurt her?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 7
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: From the publisher: “Get ready to brush up on world history with these handsome and hysterical personifications of the Axis Powers as they meet, become friends and form one of the most powerful alliances the world has ever seen.” In this volume . . . Christmas!
Title: HETALIA AXIS POWERS, VOL. 2
Author: Hidekaz Himaruya

Description: Light Yagami discovers a supernatural notebook that allows him to murder anyone he has seen by writing their name in it. He uses this ability to try to rid the world of evil.
Title: DEATH NOTE BLACK, VOL. 1
Author: Tsugumi Ohba and Takeshi Obata
Contributor: by Tsugumi Ohba and Takeshi Obata

Description: In a dark future, four individuals come together and journey to a mysterious "underground" running beneath the city on a quest for answers.
Title: DOGS, VOL. 5
Author: Shirow Miwa

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso
